Squizzy::
She waited until Feline came around.  She watched as Feline woke up 
and sat up on the table. She walked over,"How are you feeling?"

Feline2::
She looked at Feline. "I am ready for combat duty."

Squizzy:
"Excelent. Please, come with me."
Feline followed Squizzy to the doorway where Repressor was 
standing. "She's all yours."

Feline2::
She was now just as she was before. Ready to go out and seduce the 
whole of bot kind. And ready to fight and kill.  She smiled at 
Repressor. "How are you handsome?" She walked up to him, smiling 
sweetly at him and lightly brushed the tip of her long tail against 
his cheek.
